OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FThe families of three girls killed in
OL,8,Fthe Southport stabbings have said they
OL,9,Fwere "extremely alarmed" after a
OL,10,Fteenager who wanted to carry out a
OL,11,Fcopycat attack avoided a jail sentence.
OL,13,FOn Thursday 5 March, a 17-year-old boy
OL,14,Fwas sentenced at Liverpool Crown Court
OL,15,Fafter he rang police in August 2025
OL,16,Fand said he wanted to "re-enact AR",
OL,17,Fhaving collected four knives and
OL,18,Fbought a green hoodie similar to one
OL,19,Fworn by the killer.
OL,26,@qD@FOUqD@XO]xD@WOUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FIn a statement released by their legal
OL,8,Fteam on Tuesday 10 March, the families
OL,9,Fof the three girls expressed their
OL,10,Fshock and highlighted concerns,
OL,11,Fincluding that the teenager was twice
OL,12,Freferred to the Government's anti-
OL,13,Fterror programme Prevent ` but no
OL,14,Faction had been taken before his
OL,15,Farrest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FThe killer, who we are calling AR, was
OL,8,F17 when he murdered seven-year-old
OL,9,FElsie Dot Stancombe, six-year-old Bebe
OL,10,FKing and nine-year-old Alice da Silva
OL,11,FAguiar in a knife attack at a Taylor
OL,12,FSwift-themed dance class in July 2024.
OL,14,FThe Southport Inquiry heard AR was
OL,15,Freferred to Prevent on three occasions
OL,16,Fbefore carrying out his attack.
OL,18,FThe families said: "It is unimaginable
OL,19,Fto be reading about circumstances so
OL,20,Fpainfully similar to those that led to
OL,21,Fthe loss of our girls.
OL,26,@zD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,F"Elsie, Bebe and Alice were failed at
OL,8,Fevery possible point ` failed by the
OL,9,Fvery professionals and agencies who
OL,10,Fshould have protected them. Had they
OL,11,Facted decisively, our children would
OL,12,Fstill be alive.
OL,14,F"Yet we now face the reality that a
OL,15,F17yearold boy has admitted these
OL,16,Foffences, expressed ideologies aligned
OL,17,Fwith AR ` and still walks free.
OL,19,F"This is about repeated failures by
OL,20,Fagencies and professionals who knew
OL,21,Fbetter, and still did nothing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,F"Our only hope through the inquiry was
OL,8,Fthat no other families would have to
OL,9,Fendure what we have.
OL,11,F"But, the events relating to this
OL,12,Fteenager give us real concerns that
OL,13,Fchanges that we were told in have
OL,14,Foccurred, appear to fail again."
OL,16,FThe court heard the boy described AR
OL,17,Fas a "hero" with similar interests in
OL,18,F"genocides and that".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@`O]yD@FOUyD@KO]zD@AOUzD@
OL,26,ATO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FThe teenager, who cannot be named
OL,8,Fbecause of his age, was sentenced to a
OL,9,Fthree-year youth rehabilitation order
OL,10,Fand criminal behaviour order, but
OL,11,Favoided a custodial sentence after he
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to four counts of
OL,13,Fpossessing information likely to be
OL,14,Fuseful to a person planning or
OL,15,Fcommitting an act of terrorism.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FThe legal representative for the
OL,8,Ffamilies, Chris Walker from Bond
OL,9,FTurner, said: "A number of details
OL,10,Fregarding this teenager and his
OL,11,Fbackground are seriously alarming and
OL,12,Fwe felt it was only right that we
OL,13,Fcommented given the focus of the
OL,14,FSouthport Inquiry and the numerous
OL,15,Fagencies that were involved with AR
OL,16,Fprior to the events of July 2024.
OL,26,@qD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,F"The Prime Minister himself commented
OL,8,Ffollowing the Southport attack that
OL,9,Fthe institutional failings 'leap off
OL,10,Fthe page' ` and it would appear the
OL,11,Fsame can be said here."
OL,13,FHe added: "The Stancombes, Aguiars and
OL,14,FKings heard months of evidence
OL,15,Frelating to the failures and missed
OL,16,Fopportunities to prevent AR from
OL,17,Facting as he did throughout the public
OL,18,Finquiry last year, and are extremely
OL,19,Falarmed at similarities in this
OL,20,Fteenager's course of conduct.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@WO]uD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,F"We are extremely alarmed at the
OL,8,Fextremely serious fascination with
OL,9,Fmass murder, admiration for the
OL,10,FSouthport killer, and the violent
OL,11,Fmaterial and manuals reportedly found
OL,12,Fin his possession, including knives
OL,13,Fand content capable of assisting a
OL,14,Fplanned mass murderous attack.
OL,16,F"Against this backdrop, we are aghast
OL,17,Fthat a non-custodial sentence and a
OL,18,Freferral to rehabilitation services
OL,19,Fhave been considered reasonable in
OL,20,Fcircumstances of such serious risk and
OL,21,Frepeated missed opportunities.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,F"Given the information in the press,
OL,8,Fwe can not fathom why a rehabilitation
OL,9,Forder is considered the best way to
OL,10,Fprotect the public rather than a
OL,11,Fcustodial sentence.
OL,13,F"Our families have seen at first hand
OL,14,Fthe devastation caused by the
OL,15,Fincompetence of rehabilitation and
OL,16,Fsafeguarding pathways, as exposed
OL,17,Fduring the Southport Inquiry.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,F"We will be writing to Sir Adrian
OL,8,FFulford to explore this case further
OL,9,Fand find out why it appears there has
OL,10,Fbeen a further Prevent failing.
OL,12,F"The Southport Inquiry has already
OL,13,Frevealed multiple agencies in
OL,14,Fdisarray, including Prevent, policing,
OL,15,Fsafeguarding, psychiatric risk
OL,16,Fassessments, multi-agency
OL,17,Fcommunication, and escalation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773321081
OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,F"With such widespread systemic
OL,8,Ffailures, we ask: how can the public
OL,9,Fbe expected to have any confidence in
OL,10,Fthe system?
OL,12,F"The Southport families remain united
OL,13,Fin demanding accountability,
OL,14,Fmeaningful reform, and immediate
OL,15,Faction to ensure no other families
OL,16,Fendure the lifelong consequences of
OL,17,Fthese repeated systemic failures."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
