OL,3,CSouthport families 'aghast' at
OL,4,Csentence as 'copycat' teenager avoids
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FSouthport Inquiry chairman Sir Adrian
OL,8,FFulford is expected to publish his
OL,9,Freport on the first phase of the
OL,10,Fhearings next month.
OL,12,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,13,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,14,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,15,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
